Class TieBreaker

  • java.lang.Object
    • PowerUp
      • TieBreaker

  • public class TieBreaker
extends PowerUp
    TieBreaker instances represent a specific type of power-up in the game. A new instance should be created whenever the team obtains a new Tiebreaker power-up, and destroyed when the power-up is used by a hero is a villain battle.
